eference should be in hints somewhere. Since this widget extends/modifies field_pulldown, that's an important cross-reference. But V4 specifically says PascalCase class names, @Annotation names, property names from tables, and XxxException names.\n\n`field_pulldown` doesn't fit any of those categories, so it's not required by V4. That leaves just the one minor finding about missing property names in s2 hints.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":15386,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":15386,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c79a9583-ce4e-49cf-ab55-6f05d113aac3","uuid":"9e63c89d-ffe9-4e5c-9d30-fda9fd47de5e"}
